{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_10_02",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 2話 これが芽衣の目標",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ～……あれ、ここは……\nあ、そうだ！　芽衣、事務所で寝ちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fwaah~… Huh? Where am I…?\nAh‚ right! Mei fell asleep at the office…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう芽衣\nいきなり寝てしまったから驚いたぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Mei\nI was surprised because you suddenly fell asleep.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6333333969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん！\n驚かせちゃってごめんね～。でも、もう大丈夫だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san !\nSorry for startling you~. But I'm okay now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3666671117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "本当に大丈夫か？\n体調が悪そうだったらすぐに言うんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you really okay?\nIf you feel unwell‚ you have to tell me right away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "しっかり寝たから大丈夫！\nそれより、目標を決めたのに失敗しちゃったよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I slept well‚ so I'm fine!\nMore than that‚ I failed to achieve my goal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "学校でも、授業中に居眠りしちゃって\n先生に怒られちゃったし……あはは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even at school‚ I dozed off during class.\nAnd the teacher got mad at me… Ahaha.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.5666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "みんなのお手本になれるように頑張ったんだけど\nやっぱり夜更かしはしちゃダメだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I tried hard to be a role model for everyone‚ but…\nI guess I shouldn't stay up late after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.1333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "これまでの生活リズムもあると思うし\nやるにしても少しずつでいいと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it's also about your current lifestyle‚\nso I think it's okay to do it little by little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "少しずつかぁ……うーん……そうだ！\nそれなら芽衣、レッスンを増やすよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Little by little‚ huh… Hmm… That's right!\nIn that case‚ Mei will take more lessons!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.8000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "いつものレッスンだけじゃなくって、オフの日も\n怜ちゃんと、ううん、怜ちゃん以上に練習する！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not just the usual lessons‚ but even on my days off‚\nI'll practice like Rei-chan— no‚ even more than Rei-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.3333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になったばかりで、ただでさえ忙しいんだぞ？\nさすがに厳しいんじゃないか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You just became BIG4‚ and you're already busy‚ right?\nIsn't that a bit too much…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンはいつも全力でやってるから\nもっと頑張るためには回数を増やさないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I always do my best in lessons‚\nso if I want to work harder‚ I have to increase the frequency.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.9000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "その考えは立派だが、許可は出来ないな\nアイドルが無理をするのを見過ごす訳にはいかない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That thought is admirable‚ but I can't allow it.\nI can't overlook an idol pushing themselves too hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7000095368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、BIGなアイドルになったんだから\nやることも大きくしていかなくっちゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ I've become a BIG idol‚ so\nI have to make my actions bigger.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0738910518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "無理そうならすぐに止めるから\nだからお願い、挑戦だけさせて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll stop immediately if it seems too difficult‚\nSo please‚ just let me try?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.0333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、分かったよ。そこまで言うならやってみてくれ\nだが、くれぐれも無理だけはしないようにな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… okay‚ I understand. If you say so‚ go ahead and try it.\nBut‚ just make sure you don't overdo it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.2666660309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　よーし、今度こそみんなのお手本になるぞ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! Alright‚ I'll become a role model for everyone this time~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.0000401816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6999993642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.799998347
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.799998347
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nそ、そろそろ現場に行かなきゃだよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user} -san…\nS-shouldn't we be heading to the location soon…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.2333326976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……ご飯を食べるタイミングを逃したから\nお腹空いてきちゃったよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… I missed my chance to eat‚ so…\nI'm starting to get hungry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.1666660309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.3000696821
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンの後も、残って練習していたせいだな\nタクシーを使えば余裕があるし、少し休んでからいこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because you stayed behind to practice even after the lesson.\nIf we take a taxi‚ we'll have plenty of time‚ so let's rest a bit before going.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.2333326976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.0334030154
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさ～い！\n急いでドーナツ食べちゃわないと。もぐもぐもぐもぐ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry~!\nI have to eat this donut quickly. Nom nom nom nom.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.6666660309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.0333989464
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "焦らなくていいからな\nそれにしても、かなり頑張ってるみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to rush.\nBy the way‚ it seems you're working pretty hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.1999993642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ。せっかく立てた目標だったから\nちゃんと達成したいなって思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe. Since I set this goal‚\nI want to achieve it properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.4999993642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.5000788374
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "でも、お手本への道のりは長いよ。BIG4になっても\nそんなに一気に何かが変わる訳じゃないんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the road to becoming a role model is long. Even after becoming BIG4‚\nthings don't change that drastically all at once.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.0666660309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "凄いアイドルになれているのは事実だ\nそこは自信を持って誇ってもいいと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a fact that you've become an amazing idol.\nI think you can be confident and proud of that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.4999993642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 187.5334121707
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……そうかなぁ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe… Do you think so…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.5334121707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 190.966745504
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、芽衣の言う通り、すぐに何かが変わる訳じゃない\n肩書きが変わっても、芽衣は芽衣だからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ as Mei said‚ things don't change quickly.\nEven if your title changes‚ you're still Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.3999993642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "今までと変わらないかぁ……そっか、うん\nなら芽衣は、これからも今まで通り頑張っていきたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not changing from what I was before… I see‚ yeah.\nThen Mei wants to continue working hard as she has until now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.5333326976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 211.6667485558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみんなや、月ストのみんな、星見プロのみんな\nのために、歌とパフォーマンスに目一杯気持ちを込めて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For all the fans‚ Moon Tempest members‚ and all the Hoshimi Prod members‚\nI want to pour my heart into my singing and performances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.7666660309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_10_02-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になっても変わらないで\nトップアイドルを目指して進んでいきたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even after becoming BIG4‚\nI want to continue aiming to be a top idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.5666660309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 226.6334192915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
