      "text": "芽衣とか、すずにゃんとか、みんなが憧れて\nお手本にしたくなっちゃうようなアイドルに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to be an idol who can be somone's role model‚\nlike the idol that Mei‚ Suzu-nyan and everyone admire.",
