      "text": "芽衣……。そうだな、初心を忘れずに頑張る\nってことでもあるし、いい目標だと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei… That's right. That could also mean‚ working hard without\nforgetting your original intentions‚ and I think it's a good goal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.3333245595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
